<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='841241' id='t-841241'>What I hope to have shown you
in the past few minutes</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='843740' id='t-843740'>is that this isn't true.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='845325' id='t-845325'>What we need to do is assess
